oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Copy print of Jesse Land
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Land (1840-?) served in Co. H, 35th Tenn. Inf., a Confederate unit. However, he received a Federal pension for Union service, so he must have deserted and joined a Union unit. He was the son of Thomas J. Land and married Frances Hickey (born 1839).
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Land, Jesse
